# PocketBase & Base de Données

## Configuration

- **Mode**: Docker local (développement)
- **URL**: http://127.0.0.1:8090
- **Admin UI**: http://127.0.0.1:8090/_/

```bash
# Démarrage
docker run -d --name pocketbase -p 8090:8090 -v ./pb_data:/pb_data ghcr.io/muchobien/pocketbase:latest

# Vérification
curl http://127.0.0.1:8090/api/health
```

## Client Singleton

```typescript
// lib/pocketbase.ts
import PocketBase from 'pocketbase';

const pb = new PocketBase('http://127.0.0.1:8090');

// Désactiver auto-cancellation pour TanStack Query
pb.autoCancellation(false);

export default pb;
```

## Collection `events`

Créer via Admin UI (http://127.0.0.1:8090/_/) :

| Champ | Type PocketBase | Options |
|-------|-----------------|---------|
| title | text | required |
| description | text | - |
| date | date | required |
| youtube_url | url | - |
| status | select | values: draft,published,completed,cancelled ; required |
| image_url | url | - |

## Opérations CRUD

```typescript
import pb from '@/lib/pocketbase';
import type { Event } from '@/lib/types/events';

// Liste avec filtres et pagination
const events = await pb.collection('events').getList<Event>(1, 50, {
  sort: '-date',
  filter: `title ~ "${search}" && status = "${statusFilter}"`,
});

// Détail
const event = await pb.collection('events').getOne<Event>(id);

// Création
const event = await pb.collection('events').create<Event>(data);

// Mise à jour
const event = await pb.collection('events').update<Event>(id, data);

// Suppression
await pb.collection('events').delete(id);
```

## Gestion des Erreurs

```typescript
import { ClientResponseError } from 'pocketbase';

try {
  await pb.collection('events').create(data);
  toast.success('Événement créé');
} catch (error) {
  if (error instanceof ClientResponseError) {
    if (error.status === 400) {
      toast.error('Données invalides. Vérifiez les champs.');
    } else if (error.status === 404) {
      toast.error('Événement introuvable.');
    } else {
      toast.error(`Erreur: ${error.message}`);
    }
  } else {
    toast.error('Une erreur inattendue est survenue.');
  }
}
```

## TanStack Query Hooks Pattern

```typescript
// lib/hooks/use-events.ts
import { useQuery, useMutation, useQueryClient } from '@tanstack/react-query';
import pb from '@/lib/pocketbase';

export function useEvents(search: string, status: string) {
  return useQuery({
    queryKey: ['events', search, status],
    queryFn: () => pb.collection('events').getList(1, 50, {
      sort: '-date',
      filter: buildFilter(search, status),
    }),
    placeholderData: keepPreviousData,
  });
}

export function useCreateEvent() {
  const queryClient = useQueryClient();
  return useMutation({
    mutationFn: (data: EventFormData) => pb.collection('events').create(data),
    onSuccess: () => {
      queryClient.invalidateQueries({ queryKey: ['events'] });
      toast.success('Événement créé');
    },
    onError: () => toast.error('Erreur lors de la création'),
  });
}
```

## Auth (optionnel — phase avancée)

PocketBase supporte l'auth email/password et OAuth2 nativement :

```typescript
// Email/password
await pb.collection('users').authWithPassword(email, password);

// OAuth2 (Google)
await pb.collection('users').authWithOAuth2({ provider: 'google' });

// Vérifier si connecté
pb.authStore.isValid;
pb.authStore.model;
```
